Youths gathering at staircase landings during the circuit breaker appears to be a persistent problem in Tampines. These youths are known to smoke, create noise disturbances and leave behind litter.

April: https://bit.ly/2XwNa00

May: https://bit.ly/3d5B2tr

A Stomper shared these photos taken at Block 347 Tampines Street 33 after reading Stomp reports about the issue, and said residents here are facing a similar predicament.
